Puppet module: openfire

# Written by Tom McGonagle #
# mcgonagle@gmail.com
# Google Voice (617)229-5185
# http://www.puppetll.com


DESCRIPTION:
This module installs and manages openfire software
Standard and extended classes are available.
Decide and customize how you want to define configation files: static files, templates, infile modifications...


USAGE:
# Standard Classes 
include openfire              # Install and run openfire with standard configurations.
include openfire::disable     # Disable openfire service.
include openfire::disableboot # Disable openfire service at boot time, but don't stop if it's running.
include openfire::absent      # Remove openfire package.

DEPENDENCIES:
